## Current State

### What Is Working
- Full standalone deployment with API key modal and weekly budget tracker
- Full setup flow (setting ŌåÆ characters ŌåÆ conflict ŌåÆ relationships)
- Character generation with OCEAN system, wound territory weighting, vocation-free wound entries, per-slot World toggle
- Setting generation with atmosphere removal, world/conflictTexture prompt fixes, refusal handling
